{"tid":333030,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"想問一套印度電影嘅名，請有睇開嘅巴絲幫忙","createTime":"2017-07-23T12:57:27.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-25T02:38:53.000Z","uid":117552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"37722d96abab48c071e843354968e21e3ea4ae52","tid":333030,"uid":117552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T12:57:27.000Z","msg":"套電影有個類似未來戰士嘅改造人，佢捉左一個靚女去佢個基地，個基地有好多個佢嘅分身守衛。之後有個人類阿叔喬裝成佢個樣潛入機地救番個靚女。最後個改造人同班分身追殺個阿叔同個女人，點知不敵，然後剩番個頭，留左喺博物館裡面。"},{"pid":"3190cf0ffd6b7ad0f137d54330c6620cfd4e156e","tid":333030,"uid":124951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T13:09:56.000Z","msg":"Endhiran 2010<br />\n利申:未睇過,估下咋"},{"pid":"7ad0c65831951a9da68121b75ac4ce752d1feb62","tid":333030,"uid":117552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T14:06:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Endhiran 2010<br />\n利申:未睇過,估下咋</blockquote><br />\n係呢套啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"813cedab4e58a542bb7f19e8b30d0a158207c313","tid":333030,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T02:38:53.000Z","msg":"好似係叫聲震天"}]}